                "invention-title": [
                    "Water electrolysis hydrogen production system suitable for fluctuating power supply and control strategy thereof",
                    "一种用于波动性电源的电解水制氢系统及其控制策略"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a water electrolysis hydrogen production system suitable for a fluctuating power supply and a control strategy, which combine a water electrolysis hydrogen production technology with a renewable energy power generation technology, simultaneously add an energy storage battery unit, determine the electrolysis power of an electrolytic cell according to the charge state of an energy storage battery pack. Therefore, the power of the electrolytic cell is only changed among a plurality of preset powers, the safety risk caused by the fluctuation of the electrolytic power of theelectrolytic cell under the condition of a fluctuating power supply is reduced, and particularly, the combination of an alkaline water hydrogen production technology which is originally inapplicableto the fluctuating power supply and the power generation of a renewable power supply becomes possible; and the large-scale and industrial application threshold of the renewable energy water electrolysis hydrogen production technology is reduced. The method not only can prepare real green and environment-friendly hydrogen, but also can carry out peak regulation and frequency modulation on a fluctuating power supply emitted by renewable energy sources."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种适用于波动性电源的电解水制氢系统与控制策略，将水电解制氢技术与可再生能源发电技术相结合，同时增加储能电池单元，并根据储能电池组的荷电状态，确定电解槽电解功率，使得电解槽功率仅在预先设定的几个功率间变化，降低了在波动性电源条件下电解槽电解功率的波动引起的安全风险，尤其使原本不可适用于波动性电源的碱水制氢技术与可再生电源发电的联用成为可能，降低了可再生能源电解水制氢技术的规模化、工业化应用门槛。该方法不仅可以制备出真正绿色环保的氢气，也可对可再生能源发出的波动性电源进行调峰调频。"
                }
            ]
